message: Start on initial dark mode theme
User dropdown + fix base test case to accommodate package migrations.
Upgrade to Tailwind 2.0 and other refinements
Mix v6 & use RateLimiter Facade vs. trait
Select field and misc. field API refactoring
Refactor common inputs within field views to blade components for reusability.

Added API methods for defining columns for Layout and Fieldset fields. (#20)

Co-authored-by: Ryan Scherler <ryan@eastslope.studio>
Refactor all authentication and account features (#22)
Remove explicit calls to sourcemaps in markup. They are called via scripts and styles internally when bundled in prod.
Refactor dropdown to allow button as trigger
Remove custom Alpine build and recompile
Upgrading Tailwind CSS from v2 to v3

Add intersection observer to textarea component

An intersection observer provided by the @alpinejs/intersect plugin has been added to the textarea form component for better fixing wrong height on modal interactions.
